---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | AgentAI Guide" description="Privacy policy for AgentAI Guide — how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>AgentAI Guide ("we", "our", "us") operates the website agentai-guide.com. Contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@agentai-guide.com">privacy@agentai-guide.com</a></p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Analytics data:</strong> We use Google Analytics 4 to collect anonymized usage data including pages visited, time on site, and general geographic location (country/region level). This data does not identify you personally.</p>
    <p><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> If you contact us, we collect your name and email address solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>
    <p><strong>Cookies:</strong> Google Analytics sets cookies to distinguish users and sessions. You can opt out via the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To understand how visitors use our site and improve our content</li>
      <li>To respond to contact form submissions</li>
      <li>We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties for marketing purposes</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>AgentAI Guide participates in affiliate programs. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may receive a commission. Affiliate partners may set their own cookies. See our <a href="/about/">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for full details.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
    <p>If you are in the EU, UK, or California, you have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we hold about you. To exercise these rights, email <a href="mailto:privacy@agentai-guide.com">privacy@agentai-guide.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Analytics data is retained for 14 months per Google Analytics default settings. Contact form data is deleted within 90 days of resolution.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy periodically. Material changes will be noted with an updated "Last updated" date above.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
